{"data":[{"date":"18:22 12/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia 2-1 Anh: Cu\u1ed9c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft Mandzukic l\u1ea5y g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Harry Kane?</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 d\u1ef1a tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, khi Tam s\u01b0 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Tottenham \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Binh-luan-Croatia-vs-Anh-ban-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Kane b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u0111\u01b0a Anh v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh Harry Kane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd gi\u00fap Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Tunisia trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa hat-trick tr\u01b0\u1edbc Panama. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Colombia \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 anh c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Tam s\u01b0.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 4 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 10 l\u1ea7n, 6 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t ghi b\u00e0n cao h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Spurs gi\u00fap Anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t th\u1ee9 2 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u (11 b\u00e0n), ch\u1ec9 sau duy nh\u1ea5t B\u1ec9 (14 b\u00e0n). M\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Harry Kane chi\u1ebfm h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Tam s\u01b0 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n, HLV Gareth Southgate c\u00f3 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edbc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1eeb Jordan Henderson \u0111\u1ec3 trao cho trung phong \u0111ang ch\u01a1i cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Harry Kane tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eb3n v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Mario Mandzukic, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 31 b\u00e0n sau 87 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Croatia, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 anh ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Mandzukic\" title=\"Mario Mandzukic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Truoc-them-dai-chien-Anh-vs-Croatia,-Mandzukic-de-doa-Pickford--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Mandzukic ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i NHM Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu trung phong c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 c\u00f3 6 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u00ec Mandzukic m\u1edbi c\u1ecf v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 b\u00e0n. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u01a1i qu\u00e1 s\u00e2u khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n. Trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Mandzukic ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 4 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf, Mandzukic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn g\u00e1nh n\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e8 n\u1eb7ng l\u00ean vai Luka Modric.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>S\u1ef1 ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Mandzukic v\u00e0 Harry Kane</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng nay, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ecdc caro v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1eb9n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Nevilla phat bieu ve Harry Kane\" title=\"Gary Nevilla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Harry Kane\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/harry-kane-khong-the-ghi-ban-truoc-thuy-dien-va-croatia-vi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>&nbsp;Harry Kane g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-croatia-21-anh-421-190994.html\" target=\"_blank\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic</span> \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHarry Kane, ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Anh v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u01a1i v\u1eadt v\u1edd trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ea5y n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 9 ch\u1ec9 tung ra v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a trung phong 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, Mario Mandzukic, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u0103ng hoa.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 2 l\u1ea7n n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 sau nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Dele Alli v\u00e0 Kyle Walker nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn n\u00e9n \u0111au thi \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp;\u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 17 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Ph\u00fat 109, Ivan Perisic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng, anh kh\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tung ra c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00e9o g\u00f3c kh\u00f4ng cho Pickford m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Mandzukic an mung cuong nhiet sau ban thang an dinh chien thang cho DT Croatia.\" title=\"Mario Mandzukic \u0103n m\u1eebng cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0110T Croatia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mario-mandzukic-goi-chien-thang-cua-dt-croatia-la-phep-mau.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f2n Mario Mandzukic l\u1ea1i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Croatia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ghi b\u00e0n, Mandzukic c\u00f2n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c tham gia v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Croatia. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c l\u00f9i v\u1ec1 tham gia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 di chuy\u1ec3n r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng cho Rebic hay Perisic ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Mandzukic l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch 100% v\u00e0 1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra s\u1ed1 17 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 2 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMandzukic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Juventus ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1195","checkdouble":"191055"},{"date":"18:27 12/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/3-ly-do-giup-croatia-vuot-qua-anh-de-lot-vao-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn phi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga.</h2><h2>Croatia l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 khu trung tuy\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 nh\u1edd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khu v\u1ef1c trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Zlatko Dalic \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Brozovic \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Anh, \u0111\u1ea9y ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kramaric l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb d\u00f9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/182325-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Tuy\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Croatia b\u00f3p ngh\u1eb9t \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Dalic l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng. \u00d4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Croatia khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i 120 ph\u00fat \u1edf hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u knock-out tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y gi\u00fap cho Vatreni ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat v\u00e0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea9y qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean nhanh h\u01a1n khi Croatia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nRakitic v\u00e0 Modric \u0111\u00e3 tung ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n s\u00e1ng n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n b\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Ngay c\u1ea3 Harry Kane c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng lui xu\u1ed1ng h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i b\u00f3ng. Croatia \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Croatia t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ecdc th\u1ee7ng v\u00e0i l\u1ea7n trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng may m\u1eafn khi ch\u1ec9 b\u1ecb th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi 1 b\u00e0n tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHarry Kane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1eddi cho khi s\u00fat tr\u00fang c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc t\u1eeb c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. M\u1ed9t ch\u00fat b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh \u1edf pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/182411-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Croatia t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u1ecf kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng khi Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1. \u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi b\u00e0n sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Pickford \u0111\u00e3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n m\u1ecdi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a The Blazers.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, Pickford kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec khi Perisic \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Walker \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City kh\u00f4ng \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng gi\u01a1 cao ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00fat gi\u00e2y m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec3n Anh c\u00f2n t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n \u1edf hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 hai. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1eddi h\u1ee3t v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic tho\u00e1t xu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. Perisic d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y sau nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p khi\u1ebfn Tam S\u01b0 ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0110T Anh thi\u1ebfu nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Du am Anh vs Croatia\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Anh vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/DT-Anh-that-bai-vi-thieu-mot-cau-thu-sang-tao-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110T&nbsp;Anh thi\u1ebfu nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1edbi <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. M\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Lingard, Alli v\u00e0 Sterling kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m qua, \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Tam S\u01b0. Lingard l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m nh\u1ea5t khi tung ra 3 c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u00e0 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00fa s\u00fat n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111i tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlli th\u00ec ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ec7 khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu t\u1ec9 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1t 79%. Anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u00edt \u1ecfi trong kh\u00e2u tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0. Sterling th\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u00f9ng 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Ng\u00f4i sao thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Man City c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1eaft \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u1edbi 1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 74 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic-421-191055.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia 2-1 Anh: Cu\u1ed9c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1194","checkdouble":"191056"},{"date":"19:37 12/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 12/7: MU theo \u0111u\u1ed5i 1 ch\u00e0ng Cristiano kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Sporting","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-127-mu-theo-duoi-1-chang-cristiano-khac-cua-sporting.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>(ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/CHINH-THUC-Barca-chieu-mo-Lenglet-voi-gia-35-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mua xong Lenglet</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/top-5-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-tiem-nang-cua-barca-trong-he-2018-184-184650.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet</span> t\u1eeb Sevilla. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Barca ph\u1ea3i chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Sevilla. Trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Lenglet k\u00fd v\u1edbi Barcelona c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Lenglet su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p d\u00e0nh cho Los Blaugrana. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0La Liga \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Lenglet v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11, c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Lenglet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Camp Nou. Khi tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u00e0o m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lenglet \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Sevilla c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Lenglet th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Lenglet v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Sevilla v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<h2>Lenglet l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla t\u1eeb Nancy v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u0103n \u0111u\u1ed5i. Man United c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Lenglet nh\u01b0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp theo gia nh\u1eadp Barca sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ousmane Dembele, Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Sevilla, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 70 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U21. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Lenglet c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb t\u1eeb U16 \u0111\u1ebfn U21.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1193","checkdouble":"191057"},{"date":"20:04 12/07","title":"Anh thua Croatia: Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1i tim y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/anh-thua-croatia-khi-chien-thang-khong-thuoc-ve-nhung-trai-tim-yeu-duoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1ef1 b\u1ecf \u0111i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia. V\u00e0 ch\u00ednh \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd v\u1ee1 m\u1ed9ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</h2><h2>Anh t\u1ef1 thua v\u00ec k\u00e9m b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giai \u0111i\u1ec7u &quot;It's coming home&quot; cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 c\u1ee7a Anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i qua 11/7.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y r\u00f5 hai gam m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u1ea3n \u1edf m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi Croatia - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng m\u00e3nh li\u1ec7t, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh - nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1 'h\u00e8n nh\u00e1t'.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau c\u00fa s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Kieran Trippier ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi h\u1ecd \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh. Song s\u1ef1 v\u00f4 duy\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7u to\u00e0n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Anh Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1i tim y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Anh Khi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng tr\u00e1i tim y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/Nguoi-Anh-gac-lai-giac-mo-cup-vang-Bong-da-chua-tro-ve-nha,-vay-thi-da-sao-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T Anh t\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o Chung k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00ec k\u00e9m b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i hi\u1ec7p 1 l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh khi h\u1ecd t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n sau b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Trippier. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac s\u1edbm tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 h\u1ecd ch\u1eaft chiu h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Danijel Subasic.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu \u0111i c\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea7u l\u1ea1nh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ni\u1ec1m hi v\u1ecdng s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c nguy hi\u1ec3m trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n &quot;d\u1ecdn c\u1ed7&quot; c\u1ee7a Lingard. Tuy nhi\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham Hotspur \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Raheem Sterling v\u00e0 Jesse Lingard c\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 non n\u1edbt c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0nh cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 tung ra nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111o\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong hi\u1ec7p 1, sang hi\u1ec7p 2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1eb3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn cho Croatia. S\u1ef1 h\u00e8n nh\u00e1t n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng m\u00e0n t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Perisic. Gi\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Anh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nguoi-anh-tan-mong-cup-vang-sau-tat-ca-suc-tre-van-phai-chao-thua-kinh-nghiem-421-190998.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tan m\u1ed9ng c\u00fap v\u00e0ng: Sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ch\u00e0o thua kinh nghi\u1ec7m</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Football is NOT coming home!&rdquo; &ndash; Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0 sau khi \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn trong th\u1ebf b\u1ecb Croatia l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng. Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thi\u1ebfu b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng '\u0111\u00e0n anh' gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Croatia.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hi\u1ec7p 1, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 tri\u1ec3n khai l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 'l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i' h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p trong hi\u1ec7p 2. Tuy nhi\u00ean, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 l\u1ea1i ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc, b\u1ed9 3 trung v\u1ec7 Tam s\u01b0 g\u1ed3m Harry Maguire, John Stones v\u00e0 Kyle Walker \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t hi\u1ec7p 2 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a. Maguire t\u1ecf v\u1ebb ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong c\u00e1c pha tranh ch\u1ea5p, Walker th\u00ec m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung, c\u00f2n Stones l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u00e8m ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia 2-1 Anh\" title=\"Croatia 2-1 Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/sao-croatia-tuong-anh-the-nao-hoa-ra-van-vay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn Anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o v\u00e0 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong 90 ph\u00fat.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00f3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Kyle Walker. Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic v\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn Jordan Pickford kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec h\u01a1n ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phung ph\u00ed l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc b\u1eb1ng l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed9ng, \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ea5n \u00e1p v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bi th\u1ea3m. Nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 b\u1eafn v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n m\u00ecnh sau khi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong hi\u1ec7p 1.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft \u0110T Anh v\u1eabn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u0169 \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u1edf tr\u1eadn tranh gi\u1ea3i Ba World Cup 2018. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u1ea7n s\u1edbm qu\u00ean \u0111i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. HLV Southgate ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u1edf EURO 2020 hay xa h\u01a1n n\u1eefa l\u00e0 World Cup 2022.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-croatia-vuot-qua-anh-de-lot-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-466-191056.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/3-ly-do-giup-croatia-vuot-qua-anh-de-lot-vao-chung-ket-world-cup.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/3-ly-do-giup-croatia-vuot-qua-anh-de-lot-vao-chung-ket-world-cup-466-191056.html\">3 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Anh \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup</span><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn phi th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Anh v\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic g\u00e2y ch\u1ea5n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic-421-191055.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic-421-191055.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia 2-1 Anh: Cu\u1ed9c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic</span><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1eefa b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/that-bai-cua-dt-anh-tai-world-cup-2018-chi-la-bong-da-chua-the-tro-ve-466-191001.html\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1</span><br>\r\nEuro 2020 v\u00e0 World Cup 2022 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 Gareth Southgate h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean tr\u1eadn thua Croatia t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0ng gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 ch\u01b0a h\u1eb3n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, song nh\u1edd c\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Perisic v\u00e0 Mandzukic, Croatia \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c Anh v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1192","checkdouble":"191058"},{"date":"20:27 12/07","title":"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau MU sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jose Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Ivan Perisic t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Old Trafford sau khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ghi b\u00e0n khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn.</h2><h2>Perisic t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u00f4m h\u1eadn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Perisic l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a cho Croatia \u1edf tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh h\u00f4m qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n su\u00fdt gi\u00fap cho Croatia th\u1eafng ngay trong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c khi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Pickford nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ebfn hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 th\u1ee9 2, Perisic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 Mandzukic ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/mourinho-tiet-lo-ly-do-muon-dua-perisic-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho khen ng\u1ee3i Perisic sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T\u00a0Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Ivan Perisic v\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng Man United \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 ph\u00eda Inter y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t khi\u1ebfn Perisic tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cPerisic l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. B\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ec9 nhanh v\u00e0 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Nh\u01b0ng Perisic c\u00f2n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u1ecfe n\u1eefa. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng tranh b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 Perisic gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho Mandzukic ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t kh\u1ecfe. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u01a1i v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic, HLV Mourinho bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh kh\u00e1c l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez. V\u00e0 x\u00e9t theo nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Sanchez \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m khi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1ecf ti\u1ec1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Perisic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Croatia vs Anh:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-croatia-21-anh-cuoc-hoan-doi-than-xac-giua-harry-kane-va-mario-mandzukic-421-191055.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Croatia 2-1 Anh: Cu\u1ed9c ho\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e2n x\u00e1c gi\u1eefa Harry Kane v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-croatia-vs-anh-461-190987.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Croatia 2-1 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1191","checkdouble":"191059"},{"date":"20:39 12/07","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/chinh-thuc-barca-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-hau-ve-clement-lenglet.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barcelona \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet t\u1eeb Sevilla v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 35 tri\u1ec7u euro.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>(ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Lenglet v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/CHINH-THUC-Barca-chieu-mo-Lenglet-voi-gia-35-trieu-euro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Clement Lenglet</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca mua xong Lenglet</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/top-5-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-tiem-nang-cua-barca-trong-he-2018-184-184650.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Clement Lenglet</span> t\u1eeb Sevilla. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou. Barca ph\u1ea3i chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro ti\u1ec1n ph\u00ed ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Sevilla. Trong b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 Lenglet k\u00fd v\u1edbi Barcelona c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00ean t\u1edbi 300 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Lenglet su\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng tr\u1eddi v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i k\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb9p d\u00e0nh cho Los Blaugrana. T\u1eeb l\u00e2u nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110\u00a0La Liga \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i Lenglet v\u00e0 m\u1edbi tri\u1ec3n khai k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11, c\u00e1c tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Lenglet c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Camp Nou. Khi tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ea5y l\u00ean v\u00e0o m\u00f9a xu\u00e2n, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Lenglet \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, Sevilla c\u00f2n h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd bi\u1ebfn Lenglet th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Ramon Sanchez Pizjuan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Sevilla \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c khi h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Lenglet v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Sevilla v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn tr\u00ean b\u00e0n \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c Barca ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<h2>Lenglet l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Sevilla t\u1eeb Nancy v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2017, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng hot \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u0103n \u0111u\u1ed5i. Man United c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Lenglet nh\u01b0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfp theo gia nh\u1eadp Barca sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ousmane Dembele, Lucas Digne v\u00e0 Samuel Umtiti \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Sevilla, Lenglet \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n h\u01a1n 70 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp l\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 10 l\u1ea7n \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 U21. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Lenglet c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb t\u1eeb U16 \u0111\u1ebfn U21.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLenglet \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Barca m\u00f9a n\u00e0y sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Arthur Melo t\u1eeb Gremio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0o h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Hai.<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1190","checkdouble":"191060"},{"date":"23:03 12/07","title":"Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/12/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paul Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe v\u00e0 cho r\u1eb1ng ch\u00ednh anh c\u00f2n k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Mbappe \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 19.</h2><h2>Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. Anh ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u1ed9i bom h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng trong 6 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft World Cup th\u1ee9 3 trong v\u00f2ng 20 n\u0103m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi Croatia \u1edf chung k\u1ebft, Pogba \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh cho Mbappe nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/12/pogba-phat-bieu-soc-ve-mbappe.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cMbappe c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t tr\u1ebb. Ch\u00fang ta bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nghi\u1ec7p d\u01b0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y n\u00f3i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ea5u gi\u1ebfm m\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh danh hi\u1ec7u. V\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n ngh\u0129 l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cMbappe s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng trang l\u1ee9a. Nh\u01b0ng Mbappe s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00ednh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 \u0111ang gi\u00fap Mbappe t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh so v\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u khi \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00f3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<h2>Pogba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p</h2>\r\nChia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh, Pogba cho r\u1eb1ng vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a anh \u1edf tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n l\u00fac \u1edf Man United. <br />\r\n<em><br />\r\n\u201cM\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa t\u00f4i v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Deschamps l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c nhau. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 Man United c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u1ed1ng nhau. H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c nhau v\u00e0 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cNh\u00ecn chung, m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i v\u1edbi hai HLV \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n l\u1eafng nghe nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd n\u00f3i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u gi\u00fap t\u00f4i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/doi-vao-chung-ket-gap-phap-dt-anh-bi-mbappe-cuoi-vao-mat-421-191017.html\">\u0110\u00f2i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb Mbappe c\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/pogba-phat-bieu-ve-dt-phap-va-ban-than-421-191013.html\">Pogba: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u1ee9ng minh cho b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1189","checkdouble":"191061"},{"date":"06:11 13/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/19/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-conte-da-bi-chelsea-sa-thai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 13/7.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i</h2>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1edd b\u00e1o uy t\u00edn c\u1ee7a Anh nh\u01b0 BBC, Telegraph \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i th\u00f4ng tin HLV Antonio Conte s\u1ebd r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London. \u00d4ng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u00e1m \u01a1n t\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7 Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 1\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 137 Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-137-Conte-da-bi-Chelsea-sa-thai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 13/7: Conte \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Barca ch\u01a1i l\u1edbn tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t 2 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Arthur Melo v\u00e0 Clement Lenglet, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Willian. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi \u0111i, nh\u01b0ng sau khi Conte b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 anh s\u1ebd ngh\u0129 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho M.U</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 - Toby Alderweireld l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Man United v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Daily Mail, Spurs s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi kh\u1edfi tranh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho trung v\u1ec7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<br>\r\nHarry Maguire &ndash; trung v\u1ec7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 Wolrd Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Chelsea v\u00e0 M.U s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Leicester. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Ruyad Mahrez, v\u00ec v\u1eady h\u1ecd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Harry Maguire\" title=\"Harry Maguire vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/nguoi-hung-tuyen-anh-toi-dang-song-trong-giac-mo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Harry Maguire \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u1ed1t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00e2n HLV Unai Emery m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, sau khi h\u1ecd \u0111em v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 5 t\u00e2n binh t\u1eeb th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 - \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Torreira, Guendouzi, Lichtsteiner, Papastathopoulos v\u00e0 Leno.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p &ndash; TTVN</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1188","checkdouble":"191062"},{"date":"06:16 13/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (13/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-1372018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 13/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h